---
const PHONE = "+41793940167";
---
 
<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-background">
  <div class="container max-w-4xl">
    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-foreground text-center mb-12">
      Séances remboursables par certaines assurances complémentaires
    </h2>
    <div class="bg-card rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-md border border-border mb-10">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
        <!-- ASCA Badge -->
        <div class="shrink-0">
          <div class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full bg-sage-light border-4 border-primary flex flex-col items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-primary mb-1">
              <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="font-display font-bold text-primary text-lg">ASCA</span>
            <span class="font-body text-xs text-sage-dark font-semibold">Agréée</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 text-center md:text-left">
          <p class="font-body text-foreground text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Les séances de reboutologie peuvent être <strong>remboursées par certaines assurances complémentaires</strong> en Suisse grâce à l'agrément <strong>ASCA</strong> (Fondation suisse pour les médecines complémentaires).
          </p>
          <p class="font-body text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Nous vous conseillons de vérifier directement auprès de votre assurance si votre contrat prévoit une prise en charge.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 justify-center md:justify-start">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-sage-light text-sage-dark font-body font-semibold text-sm px-4 py-2 rounded-full">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/>
              </svg>
              Reconnue par les assurances
            </span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-sage-light text-sage-dark font-body font-semibold text-sm px-4 py-2 rounded-full">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
              </svg>
              Agrément ASCA
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center">
      <a
        href={`tel:${PHONE}`}
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-cta hover:bg-cta-hover text-cta-foreground font-body font-medium text-base px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors"
      >
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 0 1 4.69 13a19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 3.6 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/>
        </svg>
        Contactez-nous pour en savoir plus
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>